commandLineMenus

Interface ListItemRenderer<T>


  • public interface ListItemRenderer<T>
    Overrides the display of an item in a list. By default, the toString() function is used, but you can customize it.
    See Also:
    ListItemDefaultRenderer

      java.lang.String title(int index, T item)
      Returns the title that will be displayed.
